Package: informationeffects
Type: Package
Title: A complete pipeline for calculating information effects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kristoffer Ahlstrom-Vij
Maintainer: Kristoffer Ahlstrom-Vij <ahlstromvij@gmail.com>
Description: A complete pipeline for calculating information effects.
    It includes functions for constructing a knowledge scale from a set
    of knowledge items using IRT modeling; evaluating construct validity
    using estimated marginal means; calculating propensity scores
    for counterfactual modeling; and calculating information effects in 
    survey data using propensity scores and survey weights.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ahlstromvij/informationeffects
